description: Happy Taco brings handmade tortillas and delicious authentic Mexican food to the beautiful island of Kauai. Are you happy yet? No? That's because you haven't had your first delicious bite of Happy Taco's vegan burritos. And of course, in the grand tradition of Hawaiian taco stands, Happy Taco will serve you up some delicious fish tacos. Don't miss this great little taco truck!
name: Happy Taco
